channel.title: [TUT] Check if your Mobile phone is tracked!
channel.description:
[b][i][font=Verdana][size=72pt]Look If ur Mobile Phone is tracked ![/size][/font][/i][/b] [shadow=red,left] Step 1 .[/shadow] :
[size=10pt]Put Your mobile phone off ![/size]
[shadow=red,left]Step 2:[/shadow]
[size=10pt]Check if ur Sim-Card is inside.[/size]
[shadow=red,left]Step 3:[/shadow]
[size=10pt]Check If ur battery is inside.[/size]
[shadow=red,left] Step4:[/shadow]
[size=10pt]Put your mobile phone on ![/size]
[shadow=red,left]Step 5:[/shadow]
[size=10pt]Put your pin-code inside the form.[/size]
[shadow=red,left] Step 6:[/shadow]
[size=10pt]Press this Numbers: [b]*#06*[/b][/size]
[shadow=red,left] Step 7:[/shadow]
[size=10pt]If it worked you get a random serial code like this. 678976567899876545678[/size]
[shadow=red,left] Step 8:[/shadow]
[size=10pt]Ok if ur tracked there a "/" after the whole code something like this. 4567898776567890987665/[/size]
[shadow=red,left]Step 9:[/shadow]
[size=10pt]If ur tracked , and you want to avoid it. Get a other number and "kill" your sim card ;)[/size]
This Worked on mobiles in The Netherlands, Maby Europe , Maby all country's . [b][shadow=red,left]~Eduard[/shadow][/b]
